  "original_title": "\u2019\u0bb5\u0bbf\u0bb0\u0bc1\u0ba8\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bbf\u0ba9\u0bb0\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bb3\u0bbf\u0ba9\u0bcd \u0b87\u0bb0\u0bb5\u0bbf\u0bb2\u0bcd\u2019  94 \u0baa\u0bc7\u0bb0\u0bcd \u0b95\u0bc8\u0ba4\u0bc1",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "94 people were arrested during the 'night of the guests'",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "94 people involved in various crimes were arrested during a special raid conducted in the areas under the Badulai Police Division this morning (31).",
        "The special Sothain event, named \u201cNight of the Guests\u201d, was conducted from 3 am to 5 am.",
        "During this time, 10 people were arrested on suspicion and 32 people were ordered to be arrested by the court, three people were arrested for illegal consumption of drugs, 11 people were arrested for driving without a license and 37 people were arrested for other traffic charges.",
        "The investigation was carried out under the guidance of officers in charge of other police stations under the guidance of Padula police officer Sujith Vethamulla."
      ],
